{"tid":143502,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"跑步腳痛","createTime":"2017-03-04T16:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T04:59:55.000Z","uid":2546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4f735e5395c315af03d7c58c934be2257d5c95e","tid":143502,"uid":2546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:11:45.000Z","msg":"開始跑步無耐 跑兩三日抖一日咁<br />\n依家發覺腳爭前面痛痛地<br />\n姐係提起後爭 前面連接腳背個位就痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪要冰敷定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人明我up 乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73adf35bdc01594c4a179d60719162e6d26336a","tid":143502,"uid":85379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:17:39.000Z","msg":"腳踭前面係唔係腳掌？"},{"pid":"9e108c00ff4dfcbf502e13d3e6f1c95fa440ffdb","tid":143502,"uid":2546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:27:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>腳踭前面係唔係腳掌？</blockquote><br />\n腳掌唔痛 係腳背上少少個位痛<br />\n是咪跑步姿勢唔多好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba59ce90b6efdd4e2a37edc6f0e92661f4dcf2cd","tid":143502,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:28:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>腳踭前面係唔係腳掌？</blockquote><br />\n腳掌唔痛 係腳背上少少個位痛<br />\n是咪跑步姿勢唔多好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n先停一個星期先再講"},{"pid":"48003431f857804db14668960dc14a623f604832","tid":143502,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:30:49.000Z","msg":"韌帶過勞，抖一個星期先，仲痛嘅去睇跌打針灸"},{"pid":"ca72fd30fe9e8f6cc5071b2742bf017a59b46609","tid":143502,"uid":2546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>腳踭前面係唔係腳掌？</blockquote><br />\n腳掌唔痛 係腳背上少少個位痛<br />\n是咪跑步姿勢唔多好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n先停一個星期先再講</blockquote><br />\n咁嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽你地講抖下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6883a47fe8dd0d2f483d1f510acd08eb5a21fdf1","tid":143502,"uid":2546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:51:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>韌帶過勞，抖一個星期先，仲痛嘅去睇跌打針灸</blockquote><br />\n長遠黎講可以點解決呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為大半年前都有跑步跑到膝頭要睇鐵打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292875038c280a11fcd60600eaa7db5fff3b845a","tid":143502,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>韌帶過勞，抖一個星期先，仲痛嘅去睇跌打針灸</blockquote><br />\n長遠黎講可以點解決呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為大半年前都有跑步跑到膝頭要睇鐵打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下做腳GYM<br />\n等腳多D肌肉保護"},{"pid":"cefbe81b81f99afdb18e654628de8a180cc30375","tid":143502,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:59:55.000Z","msg":"我都試過。要休息下<br />\n<br />\n好似係筋膜放發炎"}]}